# Girl who behaves boyishly

This article discusses a particular type of [girl](/Girl) or young [woman](/Woman), often labeled as a "tomboy." For other, less precise, applications of this term, you might consult [Tomboy (disambiguation)](/Tomboy_(disambiguation)).

